buyProperty(uint256).details: Allows a user to buy a property by its ID.

params.propertyId: The unique identifier of the property to buy (0-15).

returns._0: The ID of the bought property.

getPropertyOwner(uint256).details: Retrieves the owner of a specific property.

returns._0: The address of the property owner.

getPropertyOwners().details: Retrieves the list of all property owners. This is a view function, meaning it does not modify the contract's state and can be called without incurring gas costs.

returns._0: A fixed-size array containing the addresses of all property owners. An address of 0x0...0 indicates that the property at that index is not sold.

getPropertyPrice(uint256).details: Retrieves the price of a specific property.

returns._0: The price of the property in Wei.

getPropertyPrices().details: Retrieves the list of all property prices. This is a view function.

returns._0: A fixed-size array containing the prices of all properties in Wei.
